Package organisers

Class Administrator

java.lang.Object
organisers.Employee
organisers.Administrator
public class Administrator
extends Employee
The Administrator is the one that has the ability to create threads for adding products, and to add any type of object to the auction house. Implemented based on the Singleton design pattern
